    <p class="text-justify leading-tight text-sm">
      <b>Lung Cancer:</b> We are applying multi-omics integration methods and deep learning to investigate lung adenocarcinoma
      (<i><u><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.cell.2020.06.013" target="_blank">Gillette al., Cell 2020</a></u></i>), lung squamous cell carcinoma 
      (<i><u><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.cell.2021.07.016" target="_blank">Satpathy et al., Cell 2021</a></u></i>), and
lung small cell carcinoma.
    </p>
